- This is an org primarily providing monitoring solutions

- Infrastructure monitoring

Architecture of Datadog

- the datadog agent is installed on the hosts

- the agent sends data to the cloud console

- the dashboarding, querying and visualizations is done on the console

- www.datadoghq.com

Terminologies

- agent
- dogstatsd : daemon
- statsd

- service name is "datadog-agent"
- config file: /etc/datadog-agent/*
